text: The Devil Put Dinosaurs Here is the fifth studio album by American rock band, Alice in Chains. The Devil Put Dinosaurs Here was released on May 28, 2013. The album features the singles "Hollow", "Stone", and "Voices". Guitarist Jerry Cantrell said about the album, "I don't think you'll be surprised by anything you hear. ... It's us. But it's also really unique. It's got all the elements of any record we've put out, but it's unlike any record we've put out. Basically, it's the next chapter in the Alice in Chains book, and it's going to be a big one." ==Songs== ==References== ==Other websites== *The Devil Put Dinosaurs Here at Allmusic Category:2013 albums Category:Alice in Chains albums
